Malice turned his attention from Wolfblade the Windlord and a tall femme in his doorway.  Something about her seemed familier, he stood and walked over to her.
&quot;Do I know you?&quot; he asked simply.
Organics stepped forward and peered into his red optics.  They matched, his face and voice matched, his build despite having a Maximal bnody matched, but one thing kept her from believeing he was the one she was looking for.
&quot;Perhaps.  I am looking for someone, who is family.  He has a brother fallen to darkness, and a long lost adoptive sister.  He was a Decepticon, Autobot, and some now say he is a most ruthless bounty hunter.  Do you know of anyone like this bot?&quot;
Malice stared the femme back, taking in everything she said.  Then it hit him like a freight train.  

This is his lost sister, Organics.
&quot;Organics?&quot; the bounty hunter asked.
The femme threw her arms around around his neck.
&quot;Oh Neutronics!  Where have you been?&quot;
&quot;Where have I been?  You were the one who disappeared without a trace.  How have you been in the past three hundred years?&quot;
He realized he neglected to introduce everyone.
&quot;Wolfblade, please meet my long lost sister, Organics.&quot; he said as he wheeled around and presented his half sister to Wolfblade.  

